<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<title>ʿwdy yạ frḥẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿwdy yạ frḥẗ ʿwdy ʿạdt ly ạlḥyạẗ
 ḥlny mn qywdy ( mtʿny bfdạh )2
 dwmy yạ frḥẗ dwmy yạ mḥly̱ ạltʿzyạt
 qwmy yạ nfsy qwmy hymy fy ạlbrkạt
 2- zydy yạ frḥẗ zydy qlby ạ̹tgẖyr yạ nạs
 mn ywmhạ ạ̹btdy̱ ʿydy yạ bhjẗ ạlkẖlạṣ
 3- fyḍy yạ frḥẗ fyḍy qlby ạ̹mtlạ slạm
 kẖdny bnfsh mn ạ̹ydy bnwrh mn ạlẓlạm
 4- qwly yạ frḥẗ qwly qlby sạmʿ wʿwd
 qạly yswʿ kạfyly ḥwlk ạ̉nạ mwjwd
 5- ṭyby yạ frḥẗ ṭyby qlby sjd wqạl
 ʿdy̱ ạlmṣlwb ṭbyby wḥạml ʿny ạlạ̉ḥmạl</lyrics>
</song>